        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Path to Python installation. You need to have the `latex_ocr_server` package installed, see the project's README for more information.\t\t\tNote that changing the path requires a server restart in order to take effect.",
          "target": "Python 安装路径。您需要安装 `latex_ocr_server` 包，更多信息请参阅项目的 README。\\t\\t\\t请注意，更改路径需要重启服务器才能生效。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "LatexOCR runs a python script in the background that can process OCR requests. \t\t\t\tUse these settings to check it's status, start, or stop it. \t\t\t\tNote that starting can take a few seconds. If the model isn't cached, it needs to be downloaded first (~1.4 GB).",
          "target": "LatexOCR 在后台运行一个 Python 脚本来处理 OCR 请求。 \\t\\t\\t\\t使用这些设置来检查其状态、启动或停止它。 \\t\\t\\t\\t请注意，启动可能需要几秒钟。如果模型未缓存，则需要先下载（约 1.4 GB）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Port to run the LatexOCR server on. Note that a server restart is required in order for this to take effect.",
