        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "The LatexOCR server consumes quite a lot of memory. If you don't use it often, feel free to disable this.\t\t\t\tYou will need to (re)start the server manually if you wish to use the plugin.",
          "target": "LatexOCR 服务器会消耗相当多的内存。如果您不经常使用，可以随时禁用此功能。\\t\\t\\t\\t如果您希望使用该插件，您需要手动（重新）启动服务器。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
